title: Dundalk confirmed as Irish champions
text: Dundalk confirmed as Irish champions Friday, 9 October 2015 (3 minutes ago) "We only lost one league game all season and that is a great effort," said manager Stephen Kenny as Dundalk claimed a second successive title in the Republic of Ireland.
